      • getResults

        public void getResults(java.lang.String imageUrl)
        Used to asynchronously retrieve a list of products and extended info from image url. The callbacks will be notified in case of a match for a 2D product and in case of 3D products, separately, via OnSlyceRequestListener.onResultsReceivedExt(String) and OnSlyceRequestListener.onResultsReceived(JSONObject) and OnSlyceRequestListener.onImageDetected(String) , accordingly. 2D match is possible for Premium and 2D-enabled users only. In case of a 2D match, additional info might be delivered, via OnSlyceRequestListener.onImageInfoReceived(JSONArray) callback.
        Specified by:
        getResults in interface com.android.slyce.interfaces.SlyceRequestInterface
        Parameters:
        imageUrl - The url of the image to recognize.

      • getSimilarFromResults

        public void getSimilarFromResults(java.lang.String imageUrl)
        For Premium Users Only. Used to asynchronously retrieve a list of products and extended info similar to the image passed with the URL. Calling this method will begin the visual 3D recognition of the image that is passed with the URL and will retrieve similar products based on that image. The callbacks will be notified in case of a match for a 3D products, via OnSlyceRequestListener.onResultsReceivedExt(String) and OnSlyceRequestListener.onResultsReceived(JSONObject), as well as the progresses via OnSlyceRequestListener.onProgressExt(String)} and OnSlyceRequestListener.onSlyceProgress(long, String, String)}
        Specified by:
        getSimilarFromResults in interface com.android.slyce.interfaces.SlyceRequestInterface
        Parameters:
        imageUrl - The URL of the image object we would like to recognize.
